Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where was it?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What? What?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't know how to get there?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In that case, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see... this way!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've already passed through here.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's this way, then!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've been here already...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, here!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.62,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over there!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This way!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're completely lost.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if Ooshige-san will come pick me up.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you lost?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, you're... {a devil in disguise}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We met at the Seed Record audition, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you for your help back then.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.00,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That is...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... didn't know anyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and when I was feeling lonely... you talked to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess so.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Congratulations on that earlier accomplishment.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way... where are you headed?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This place.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If that's where you're going, you should take the train to the next station...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and from there, it'll be faster to just walk.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll write it down on your map.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.89,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...do people go that far for others just like that? {shani: what are you saying Meroko?}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here you go.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll do as you said, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.26,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You trust others too much, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}. {Yeah, that's kind of her weakness of sorts}
