Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't hurry, it'll start!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.58,Note,,0,0,0,Sign,{\fs300\c&HFEF6FA&\shad0\bord0\fscx275\fscy105\pos(186,98)}I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.58,Notice 03 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be2\an5\bord1\pos(186,262)\fscx84\fscy169}Mermaid \NTear \N{\fs16}Commercial \NAudition \NRoom
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.28,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're late, you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.27,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I got lost...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I would have picked you up if you had called...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I met this nice person on the way who gave me directions.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}From Shinbashi...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shinbashi?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You came from Shinbashi?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It says to get off at Yurakucho, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why...?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's that girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like you managed to get here in one piece.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That was mean of you!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was just playing around.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't expect you to actually believe me...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess you could call it payback for before.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Payback?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...said you didn't have connections...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but you obviously did, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Totally in the dark...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I said all that with the intention of winning...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I really didn't have any connections!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.08,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if that's true.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In that case... why don't we try this.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do this fair and square.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's with that girl?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's Real Music's Wakamatsu Madoka.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As far as I know...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's your biggest rival for this audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.97,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're going to keep playing dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.66,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.39,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...must have looked like a total fool.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.02,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But just you watch, {\i0}Full Moon{\i1}!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.96,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone like you...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.02,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll take you down to your knees!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The other rivals are...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're all rivals.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're all people I've seen on TV or in magazines.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's Wakamatsu Madoka?!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't notice it until you mentioned it.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was so ordinary when she was a child actor.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(90,450)}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(255,450)}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's almost like she's a completely different person.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Could it be that she had plastic surgery?! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... she sure cleaned up nicely.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I couldn't possibly be like her.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.29,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.67,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's been in show business since she was little...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.94,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What an amazing person...{now's not the time to compliment your raibaru}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.20,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if someone like me can beat her...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you so nervous about?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To help you out during the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll give you advice.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.15,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be sure to respond sincerely and distinctly.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.32,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In any case, just relax.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stand up straight.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your answers should be clear and snappy.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look straight into their eyes while you're talking.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, ma'am! {The "yes sir" thing even when referring to a woman is an annoying epidemic still plaguing fansubs today}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.21,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Very good.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go then!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.13,0:11:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.10,0:11:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The door won't open!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is it broken?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is anyone there?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.48,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was sure she'd be here, \Nnow where'd that Mitsuki go?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The audition's about to start.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where'd you run off to?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The bathroom door wouldn't open...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways... at least you made it in time.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is the new concept that they just handed out for their product.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look it over at least once.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's that girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She had to be the one who did it!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.17,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just jump to conclusions like that! {Edited from "Don't just assume whatever you want!"}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Also... you will be interviewed in pairs.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's how the judges have decided to do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... that's who you'll be with...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The person over there seems happy about it for some reason...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't lose!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.07,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's almost time...  {I added a new color style for Takuto in this case, check the style sheet}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.97,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why am I worrying about it?! {Takuto as Mitsuki is still awkward}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After the people ahead of you come out...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...please go in and take their places. {and take their...}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(465,450)}{\pos(420,450)}Okay! {madoka}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(275,450)}{\pos(420,450)}Okay!{Furu muun}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.97,Notice 04 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\fscx90\fscy136\pos(317,107)}Mermaid \NTear {\fs34}\NCommercial \NAudition \NRoom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.97,Block,,0,0,0,Sign,{\fs290\alpha00\fscx397\fscy216\c&HEFE1DB&\pos(317,225)}I
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.65,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm finally here...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm totally positive that what happened in the bathroom...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...was all her doing.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still talking about that...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You managed to get out, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See! Look!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So she did do it!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is there someone that you like?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.36,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's trying to make you lose your composure before the interview!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What difference does it make if there is one?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.16,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The worst thing that can happen to someone doing commercials is a scandal.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The image of the product would be instantly ruined.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...if a scandal were to happen during the contract period...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The company behind the commercial would, of course...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...terminate the deal accordingly.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should we do then?! {The person, or in this case, Shinigami giving advice is wondering what to do, lol} {shani: Meroko <3 totally took the bait!}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.99,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's lost her confidence now.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if Meroko can handle it...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course, I use Mermaid Tear shampoo every day!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All the beauty parlors say Mermaid Tear is great.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all I've used since!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.80,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.80,0:14:30.55,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I came, despite not knowing a thing about the product...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.56,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they ask me... what should I say...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be2}Your purity is your strength, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be2\fad(0,300)}So just say how you feel truthfully.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.94,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just tell them how I feel truthfully?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't look so uneasy.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll come up with the perfect thing to say!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko... that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And... what about you, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.24,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(390,450)}Ah.{Furu muun}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.24,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(545,450)}Ah. {Meroko}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How do you fit the shampoo's image?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.04,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That is...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ever since I was little, I've always wanted hair that would bounce!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:06.26,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bounce, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Fire!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh crap!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's too strong!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop it, Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm trying!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...please excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This isn't really anything...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Enough!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... it stopped.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}U-Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't it bouncy?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're quite funny.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.09,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That wasn't funny at all... {lighten up}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.93,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or something like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.40,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even that worked?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.20,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, that's it for the interview.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(190,450)}Thank you very much! {Furu muun}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(475,450)}Thank you very much! {Madoka}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... by the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shouldn't you tell them about {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You have someone that you like, right? {Low-blow, I cry foul}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How could she say that at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I said it out loud!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uh... not really...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.05,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone that she likes...?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Say that you don't have one!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cover it up!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cover it up...?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}But we can't see the moon when it's covered up.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Even if you can't see it...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}The power of the moon will show you the way.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}So, on nights like these... just close your eyes...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Listen to the sound of the waves...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You can still feel the moon up in the sky, can't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.17,0:17:09.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Do you feel it?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.13,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Then the moon can't play hide and seek anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.48,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it's for the promise I made with Eichi-kun... {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.19,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why do I have to hide it?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.78,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hiding it feels like it'd be wrong...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.69,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's the truth, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.99,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There is!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's someone I like! {There's also someone I like, and that is sleep, I was up at 1 am at the time of this writing, lol}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh man...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's the worst thing for an image... {and a bitter, spiteful broad is a good imejii}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.12,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That'll be the end for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.29,Notice 04 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\frz357.3\frx2\fry14\org(319,147)\pos(364,158)}Mermaid         Tear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.29,Notice 04 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\frx2\fry14\pos(365,293)\org(314,285)\frz358.7}Commercial     Audition
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.29,Notice 04 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\frx2\fry14\frz359\pos(453,359)\org(325,351)}Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.29,Notice 04 (Episode 16),,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\frx2\fry14\frz359\org(178,345)\pos(198,360)}Waiting
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You told them?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.29,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well... it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's just how you are, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So it doesn't look too good, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just one audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay... bye.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko couldn't pull it off after all... {it wasn't Meroko's fault, props to Mitsuki for honesty}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Meroko, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I got a phone call... from Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto? What'd he say?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He said not to worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.12,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.67,0:18:34.21,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I didn't tell him you mentioned Eichi-kun during the interview. {Shani: Meroko has always been so nice T_T}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We would like to congratulate everyone on a job well done.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, now I'll announce the results of the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh... the judges have decided...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Image Character for Mermaid Tear will be...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Real Music's Wakamatsu Madoka-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much! {XP}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.85,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.38,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This makes us even for the last time...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.69,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... we're not done yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Village Pro's {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You also fit the commercial image perfectly.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.45,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Way to go, Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's all.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We'll change the setup of the commercial...
