Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so glad that I get to work with you!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please, just choose one of us!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
