Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.31,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why did you tell Mitsuki that \Nyou were once a human?!{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shove it!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's my choice to make!
